    DEFINE BUFFER bf-job-hdr FOR job-hdr.
    DEFINE BUFFER bf-oe-ordl FOR oe-ordl.
    DEFINE BUFFER bf-itemfg  FOR itemfg.

    FIND FIRST users WHERE
